Description.Name: AC2 QS Ammo
Description.Details:
Quicsell brand ammunition is guaranteed to be able to deliver higher potential damage than normal ammunition or your money back!* 

 <size=80%> *Damage may vary from round to round, warranty void upon firing. <size=100%> 

 Upon receiving a Critical Hit, any remaining ammunition stored inside an Ammo Bin will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
